      "content": "Interesting. So you're saying the \"NIMBY\" concerns are basically just people being stuck in the past? It seems like a lot of people are worried about things like rising rents and displacement when these big developments go in, though. Is that just another part of the \"outdated\" mindset you mentioned, or is there some weight to those concerns?",
